name: Tsurime eyes - Concept LoRA
description:
Indroduction:

Tsurime eyes - a particular style of drawing eyes in Anime where the outer corners point upward, ending in a distinct point, used in contrast to the traditional Moe Moe soft drooping style,

Tsurime symbolizes strong will, arrogance, or pride in a character. Most noticeable in female designs (since it plays against the stereotype) and is commonly an attribute of tsunderes, kuuderes and particularly badass action girls.

Model used for previews: DivineAnimeMix (soon)

Recommendations:

  • 1.0 weight

  • tsurime as an activation tag

Suggested regular prompt:

  • (tsurime:1.2) in your positive prompt

Credits:

Trained on NAI Anime Full. Dataset of 1000 pictures. 10 Epochs. Clip Skip - 2.

Really BIG thanks to:

  • Me, for not being lazy

  • Some good folks from Discord server

  • You, for reading, downloading and reviewing this LoRA
